setLAF

public void setLAF(java.lang.String lookAndFeelStr)
As a convenience, allow config file to specify "Metal" or Nimbus". Absence of the parameter results in default to Metal. Otherwise, the config file must provide a fully qualified LAF name.

Parameters:
